Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 6.13 05/24] HID: pidff: Add MISSING_DELAY quirk and its detection
Date: Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:53:45 -0400
Message-Id: <20250331145404.1705141-5-sashal@kernel.org>
